---
title: Quick Irish-Style Turkey Stew with Garlic Crostini
description: In this hearty twist on a classic potato and turkey stew, we've swapped in quick-cooking ground turkey so your meal will be on the table in less than 40 min. Don't forget to wipe the bowl clean with a slice of garlic crostini!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-dinde-a-lirlandaise-cac82537.jpg
